### Source code

This is the code that is used to end a POST to the endpoint:

```
public async Send(endpoint: string, payload: any | null = null, includeHeaders = true): Promise<APIResponse> {
	try {
		const headers = this.AuthClient.GetAuthHeader(this.apiType, "application/json");
		const options = {};
		if (includeHeaders) {
			options["headers"] = headers;
		}
		if (payload) {
			options["data"] = payload;
		}
		const ctx = await request.newContext({ baseURL: this.apiUrl });
		const response = await ctx.post(endpoint, options);
		return response;
	}
	catch (error) {
		console.error("Error occurred:", error);
		throw error;
	}
}
```

**Steps**

